@startuml
left to right direction

AudioPlaybackService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioUploadService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioCatalogoService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioValidarService - [Componente Áudio]
AudioPlaybackService ..> [Componente Usuário]: "tocarAudio()"
AudioValidarService ..> [Componente Uploader]: "validarFormato()"
AudioUploadService ..> [Componente Uploader]: "fazerUpload()"
AudioCatalogoService ..> [Componente Usuário] : "buscarAudio()"
AudioCatalogoService ..> [Componente Usuário] : "listarAudiosUploader()"
AudioCatalogoService ..> [Componente Usuário] : "listarAudiosUser()"
@enduml